---
alwaysApply: true
---

This is a Base44 platform app. Follow these strict rules:
- NEVER modify /components/ui/ files — these are platform UI primitives
- NEVER change routing logic — auth/routing is handled by Base44 infrastructure
- NEVER remove or rename entity fields in entities/*.json without explicit instruction
- NEVER add new npm packages without asking first
- Use only these packages: react, tailwind, shadcn/ui, lucide-react, recharts, react-query, date-fns, framer-motion, lodash, react-router-dom, sonner
- All data access must use: import { base44 } from '@/api/base44Client'
- Pages MUST be flat — never create pages/subfolder/Page.js
